VodaText,is,an,SMS,delivery,service,that,provides,bulk,SMS,services,in,multiple,languages,They,can,deliver,to,mobile,networks,covering,countries,Users,can,get,delivery,reports,to,confirm,the,delivery,of,messages,in,real,time,as,well,as,receive,replies,to,messages,in,their,inboxes,VodaText,also,provides,a,number,validation,service,for,checking,the,status,of,mobile,numbers,Users,can,access,VodaText,s,messaging,capabilities,programmatically,via,REST,API